    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The Vue InstantSearch for Vue 3 umd build doesn't have the plugin builtin, as in general you want to pick and choose which files you want included. However rewriting the plugin yourself is really simple: \r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst VueInstantSearchPlugin = {\r\n  install(localVue) {\r\n    Object.keys(VueInstantSearch).forEach((widgetName) => {\r\n      localVue.component(\r\n        VueInstantSearch[widgetName].name,\r\n        VueInstantSearch[widgetName]\r\n      );\r\n    });\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n```\r\n\r\nhttps://codepen.io/Haroenv/pen/LYarZJp",
